{"tid":322830,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[治癒系文青]Hip Hop介紹系列- Triple G","createTime":"2017-07-15T06:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T19:10:03.000Z","uid":84384,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08c5be2bc2b526c71cd48b8b7aa74aa9775dd1e6","tid":322830,"uid":84384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T06:57:02.000Z","msg":"介紹過撒野作風既Youngqueenz 後今次想介紹旗下一位風格低調 柔情似水既rapper - Triple G<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hcMihL4l9IU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhcMihL4l9IU&d=eue%2FMUzPyBi8wleLr1e%2Fc9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b24a13a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hcMihL4l9IU</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單既韻律 舒服寫意既用詞 打造出獨有既文青感 Hip Hop本來就冇佢既界限 Triple G都冇刻意去搵主流既類型做創作 三年黎一直做同樣風格既音樂 個人幾喜歡「火花」呢首作品<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AmO7rAoKaBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAmO7rAoKaBY&d=eue%2FMUzPyBi8wleLr1e%2Fc9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=2b6a388e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AmO7rAoKaBY</a><br />\n<br />\n獨立製作既好處係唔需要似主流音樂咁一式一樣<br />\n火花再零零碎碎既畫面集合埋一齊 未必需要誘發觀眾思考 但會自然同舒服地投入佢既聲音 安撫日常焦躁不安既情緒 讓自己好好重新出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而本年都成功推出左個人專輯 淺藍色的號角 有興趣聽既可以係spotify度聽晒所有作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n火花會閃耀<br />\n係被刺痛先會閃耀既夢"},{"pid":"f012434a1694a89e31ae484ce01671f512ef5f35","tid":322830,"uid":84384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f85a14b3139e2dd71120cdbecb61be365c662cf","tid":322830,"uid":84384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0afa486b2420fcf1a42cbc099e4d005735d19acd","tid":322830,"uid":84384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:54: